comment: /**  * Returns the name of the command.  * @return the command's name  */
code: /**  * Returns the name of the command.  * @return the command's name  */ String getName().

comment: /**  * Returns a description of the command.  * @return the command's description  */
code: /**  * Returns a description of the command.  * @return the command's description  */ String getDescription().

comment: /**  * Returns usage help for the command. This should be a simple one-line string  * describing basic usage. e.g. '[options] &lt.file&gt.'. Do not include the name of  * the command in this string.  * @return the command's usage help  */
code: /**  * Returns usage help for the command. This should be a simple one-line string  * describing basic usage. e.g. '[options] &lt.file&gt.'. Do not include the name of  * the command in this string.  * @return the command's usage help  */ String getUsageHelp().

comment: /**  * Gets full help text for the command, e.g. a longer description and one line per  * option.  * @return the command's help text  */
code: /**  * Gets full help text for the command, e.g. a longer description and one line per  * option.  * @return the command's help text  */ String getHelp().

comment: /**  * Returns help for each supported option.  * @return help for each of the command's options  */
code: /**  * Returns help for each supported option.  * @return help for each of the command's options  */ Collection<OptionHelp> getOptionsHelp().

comment: /**  * Return some examples for the command.  * @return the command's examples  */
code: /**  * Return some examples for the command.  * @return the command's examples  */ Collection<HelpExample> getExamples().

comment: /**  * Run the command.  * @param args command arguments (this will not include the command itself)  * @return the outcome of the command  * @throws Exception if the command fails  */
code: /**  * Run the command.  * @param args command arguments (this will not include the command itself)  * @return the outcome of the command  * @throws Exception if the command fails  */ ExitStatus run(String... args) throws Exception.
